Test Datasets:
  Reasonable window widths for the given data range from 31 to 60. A
  default of 3*sigma for outlier- and 2*sigma for shift detection
  should be used.

  signal1.txt - cutoff sawtooth
  serie1n.txt - signal1 + N(0,1) noise
  serie1t.txt - signal1 + T(3) noise

  signal2.txt - two triangles
  serie2n.txt - signal2 + N(0,1) noise
  serie2t.txt - signal2 + T(3) noise

  signal3.txt - piecewise smooth sine with one shift
  serie3n.txt - signal3 + N(0,1) noise
  serie3t.txt - signal3 + T(3) noise
